### ========================================
### Django API Direct Gateway Tests
### ========================================

### Test Django API via Gateway - Get Companies (General Module)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/django-api/api/general/companies/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

### Test Django API via Gateway - Get Company by ID
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/django-api/api/general/companies/1/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

### Test Django API via Gateway - Create Company
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/django-api/api/general/companies/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "name": "Direct Django Test Company",
  "address": "789 Django Street"
}

###

### Test Django Swagger Docs via Gateway
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/django-api/docs/general/
Accept: text/html

###

### Test Django API Direct (without gateway) - for debugging
GET http://localhost:8000/api/general/companies/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

