### ========================================
### Python Integration Service Tests (.NET calling Django)
### ========================================

### Get All Companies from Django (via .NET service)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/pythoncompanies
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

### Get Company by ID from Django (via .NET service)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/pythoncompanies/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

### Create Company in Django (via .NET service)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/pythoncompanies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "name": "Test Company from .NET",
  "address": "123 Test Street",
  "phone": "+1-234-567-8900",
  "email": "test@company.com"
}

###

### Update Company in Django (via .NET service)
PUT {{API_HostAddress}}/api/pythoncompanies/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "name": "Updated Company Name",
  "address": "456 Updated Avenue"
}

###

### Partial Update Company in Django (via .NET service)
PATCH {{API_HostAddress}}/api/pythoncompanies/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "name": "Partially Updated Name"
}

###

### Delete Company from Django (via .NET service)
DELETE {{API_HostAddress}}/api/pythoncompanies/1
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

### ========================================
### Hybrid Controller Tests (SQL + Django)
### ========================================

### Get Companies from Both Sources (.NET SQL + Django API)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/hybridcompanies/all-sources
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

### Sync Company from .NET Database to Django
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/hybridcompanies/sync-to-django/1
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

### Compare Company Between .NET and Django
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/hybridcompanies/compare/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

